					<div class="highlight-card">
						<h3>Current Grant</h3>
						<p>European Space Agency Network of Resources grant (‚Ç¨4,215) for Pannonian water temperature analysis</p>
						<a href="/research" class="highlight-link">Learn More ‚Üí</a>
					</div>
					<div class="highlight-card">
